<A NAME="name()"><!-- --></A><H3>
name</H3>
<PRE>
public abstract <A HREF="http://java.sun.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/String.html?is-external=true" title="class or interface in java.lang">String</A>[] <B>name</B></PRE>
<DL>
<DD>The name of this bean, or if plural, aliases for this bean. If left unspecified
 the name of the bean is the name of the annotated method. If specified, the method
 name is ignored.
<P>
<DD><DL>
